	MEAutoStart works like the AutoStart-function from
	Windo*s 95/98.
	But MEAutoStart can more:
	- For each Disk you can define, a script or program, which
	  will run if you insered, or remove.
	- You can disable the start from defined disks
	- It works with Disk, CDs, HDs,...
	- It is an Commodity with GUI

	NOTE: The build-in language is GERMAN, please
	install the english catalog-file (with the included
	installer-script) to use the english-GUI!
	More infos about the catalogs, in the Catalogs.guide.

@ENDNODE

