@NODE Hersteller " CD-Manufactor/Reseller"

	I hope some CD-Manufactor and Reseller copy a MEAutoStart
	File on there CD, this files are:

	 @{b}For insert:@{ub}
		MEAutoStart.Run:
		 The program with this name will start as wb-program.
	      @{b}or:@{ub}
		MEAutoStart.File:
		 The program with this name will start as shell-program.
		(If this file have a set S-Flag, the file will
		 also run)

	 @{b}For remove:@{ub}
		MEAutoEnde.Run:
		 The program with this name will start as wb-program.
	      @{b}or:@{ub}
		MEAutoEnde.File:
		 The program with this name will start as shell-program.
		(If this file have a set S-Flag, the file will
		 also run)

@ENDNODE


